        <abstract> 
<p>Glad to hear of new German edition of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>. He is revising the English edition, adding a new chapter of "Answers".</p>  
<p>No new edition of <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi> has appeared.</p>  
<p>Would be glad to see a new translation of the <hi rend="italic">Journal of researches</hi>, which he revised in 1845.</p> 
            <p>Comments on white colour of sea-birds.</p>
        </abstract>
